name: Arthur McGregor
summary:
Arthur McGregor is a 31-year-old Software Engineer based in Los Angeles, California. He originally hails from Chicago and studied at New York University. Being outdoorsy, he maintains an active lifestyle and places importance on fitness. Arthur values honesty, adventure, and fitness. He loves coding, watching and playing football, and traveling. Despite his love for adventures, he's looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship. 

Arthur is an agnostic and holds moderate political views. He is fluent in both English and Spanish, and while he doesn't have kids, he'd love to in the future. He is an INTP, a Gemini, and owns a dog. He drinks socially, and doesn't use any drugs. 

Arthur seeks a partner in the age range of 25-35 who lives an active lifestyle and who doesn't smoke or use marijuana. His potential partner should want to have children in the future.
